Love the game like all the others... But the main question is how to get a mate and I will answer that for you guys! So on the map find a picture of a wolfs head and run to it... When you get there howl (or bite the wolf) and keep biting it until it says bond under the wolfs health and click it. The it will ask you to match the pitches of the howls ( this might help you) get to know the howls and then bond with the wolf. Oh I forget to tell you this under your wolfs health hunger a thirst you will see 4 slots to get a mate you need to have one of those slots has to be unlocked. I hope this helped! ;-)

To get a pack, you must match the notes, in other words, match the pitches of the howls that the other wolf makes. Say the wolf says 534, you must copy that exact same pattern or else you won't get the wolf into your pack. So to get it you must basically match the pitches of the wolfs howls. I hope this helps you guys.
